    <h1 id="title ">Narendra Modi</h1>
<h2 class="text-center  text-primary ">The Prime Minister Of India</h2>
<center><image src="https://images.yourstory.com/cs/2/656f3140-2d6a-11e9-aa97-9329348d4c3e/modi21566395808728.png?fm=png&auto=format" alt="PM Modi that inspire the youth and remind us why we need to support their ideas and entrepreneurial zeal." class="img-center-blocked img-responsive img-rounded shadow"></center>
   
