  </div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="well">
        <h3 class="text-center">CORNER FACTS</h3>
<div style="border:5px double deepskyblue ;">
 <ul class="connected list no2">

   <li><strong>NAME</strong>- Narendra Modi.</li>
   <li><strong>FULL NAME</strong>- Narendra Damodardas Modi</li>
     <li><strong>BIRTH DATE</strong>- September 17, 1950</li>
<li><strong>PLACE OF BIRTH</strong>- Vadnagar, India</li>
<li><strong>SPOUSE</strong>- Jashodaben Narendrabhai Modi</li>
     <li><strong>EDUCATION</strong>- Gujarat University, Delhi University</li>
<li><strong>OCCUPATION</strong>- Prime Minister</li>
